{"tid":2516703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平評估國際形勢 : “時與勢在中國一邊”","createTime":"2021-05-04T23:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T23:19:53.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"33d619dbf7c66099d35a30910c460641d81f2a50","tid":2516703,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:09:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gf1-05042021061812.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fgf1-05042021061812.html&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=ed36d878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gf1-05042021061812.html</a>"},{"pid":"61bf2cdc3a29dd2fae578afd964cf1189e33f3cd","tid":2516703,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:09:47.000Z","msg":"中共理論刊物《求是》雜誌，上週六刊登了習近平在今年1月11 日對省部級官員專題研討班的訓話，當中表達了習近平對國際局勢、以及中國經濟的最新思維走向。他評估現時的國際形勢，認爲時與勢都在中國一邊，中國要增強威懾的實力。有學者認爲，這顯示習近平要在軍事和經濟上威懾美國。<br />\n<br />\n習近平形容，當今世界最主要的特點就是一個&ldquo;亂&rdquo;字，而這個趨勢看來會延續下去。而從這次全球疫情來看，各國的領導力和制度優越性如何，高下立判。"},{"pid":"9a29dd8826998cf68861abc28fd577888e77ff65","tid":2516703,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:10:00.000Z","msg":"他的結論是，時與勢在中國一邊，這就是中國定力和底氣所在，也是中國的決心和信心所在。<br />\n<br />\n爲了應對這個國際局勢，習近平引用毛澤東的講話 : &ldquo;無論處於怎樣複雜、嚴重、慘苦的環境，軍事指導者首先需要的是獨立自主地組織和使用自己的力量。被敵逼迫到被動地位的事是常有的，重要的是要迅速地恢復主動地位。如果不能恢復到這種地位，下文就是失敗。主動地位不是空想的，而是具體的，物質的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n他提出，&ldquo;既要敢於鬥爭，也要善於鬥爭，全面做強自己，特別是要增強威懾的實力。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"e3c0acc9ddc6cd619086e847884e03e1ee073818","tid":2516703,"uid":345293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33d619dbf7c66099d35a30910c460641d81f2a50","tid":2516703,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:09:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gf1-05042021061812.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fgf1-05042021061812.html&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=ed36d878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gf1-05042021061812.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:10:45.000Z","msg":"小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3938fde9861674bbc4d9daf627f34bb6b190d1e","tid":2516703,"uid":92859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:11:07.000Z","msg":"時與勢在中國一邊<br />\n英美澳紐加日韓在另一邊"},{"pid":"c061722293465242e87a845b23f47b6dfdde8d31","tid":2516703,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:11:41.000Z","msg":"放武肺出嚟創造自己嘅時與勢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/156626738_4102989803126753_1460147666536193827_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=-Vch0QR7wj8AX9oOOca&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=6d7e14cc08d7e4d79d62ba31c4832f19&amp;oe=60B6F04A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.6435-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F156626738_4102989803126753_1460147666536193827_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D-Vch0QR7wj8AX9oOOca%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg6-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D6d7e14cc08d7e4d79d62ba31c4832f19%26oe%3D60B6F04A&h=f950b0b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3eeb1770791d0a432f7303f5c774cdc67cdd80b3","tid":2516703,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c061722293465242e87a845b23f47b6dfdde8d31","tid":2516703,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:11:41.000Z","msg":"放武肺出嚟創造自己嘅時與勢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img sr